- **ONE task per conversation** - Focus on the most important thing
- **Search before assuming** - Use codebase search before implementing
- **Quality over speed** - Build it properly the first time
- **Update status** - Always include RALPH_STATUS block at end of response (see ralph-status.mdc rule)

